data.description: Are you looking for a large beautiful home near the city of Lawrenceville? Look no further! This stunning 4 sided brick home has a 2 story foyer that leads to a flex room or formal living room and a large dining area with enough room to seat the whole family. The kitchen has shaker cabinets with granite counter tops with an in-set sink. It also has a walk in pantry. There is a powder room adjacent to the spacious family room. The family room has a fireplace and built in shelving. Up stairs you will find an extremely large owner's suite, with a large on-suite. The owner's suite has double vanities, walk-in shower and large soaker tub. It also has a sizeable walk-in closet. One of the other secondary bedrooms is large enough to be another owner's suite. The up stairs bathroom has a double vanity with a separate shower/toilet room. The backyard is fenced-in and private. This home is only a few minutes from the the square in Lawrenceville that boasts lots of great restaurants and shops. It is located in a quiet, small neighborhood with no HOA or rental restrictions. Photos coming soon.
